videos.headline: BC strikes first with 3-yd TD
videos.description: AJ Dillon squeezes into the end zone for a 3-yard Boston College TD, giving the Eagles an early lead.

videos.headline: Virginia Tech answers quickly with 26-yd TD
videos.description: Ryan Willis finds Damon Hazelton for a 26-yard Virginia Tech touchdown.

videos.headline: Hokies take first lead of game with 4-yd TD pass
videos.description: Ryan Willis connects with Eric Kumah for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Grimsley reaches back for one-handed grab
videos.description: Hezekiah Grimsley is able to somehow get one hand on the ball and hold on for a first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Virginia Tech’s Grimsley reaches back for one-handed grab) 2018/11/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hokies take advantage of the Eagles' stumble, recover fumble
videos.description: Boston College's Anthony Brown fumbles the ball at the Virginia Tech 35-yard line and after appearing to recover it he loses control again.

videos.headline: Levy runs through the pack for a 29-yard BC touchdown
videos.description: Travis Levy finds a wide-open lane and puts on the jets for a Boston College touchdown.

videos.headline: Sebastian comes up with pick after multiple deflections
videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Ryan Willis has his pass defected a number of times and it's Brandon Sebastian that comes up with the ball for Boston College.

videos.headline: Levy's second effort puts 6 on the board for BC
videos.description: Travis Levy is initially blocked from flying over the pile into the end zone, but he takes a moment and scores on the second attempt.

videos.headline: Turner's sweet catch in end zone closes gap on BC
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Ryan Willis lets it fly 14 yards to Tre Turner who hauls in the touchdown pass to come within a score of Boston College.
